{"author":{"id":"59aa60c6b459be9253b73bffbdf2b7897a48f23f8e10c462bf777983a6ea4796"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1559721511,"nonce":"aMoLt+nFbx4XVsZkdlUT6z62rjU=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0NTIzNjMwMDg=","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/2441","origin":"github"},"title":"JBrowse: cannot use callbacks in style options","message":"It is not possible to use callbacks in track config style.label and style.description because special characters as single quote and curly brackets are sanitized and are not mapped back in the trackList.json.\n\nFor example this style.description value (used to get the \"note\" attribute of the parent feature)...\n`function(featureObject,value) { return featureObject.parent().get('note')}`\n...gives this nonfunctional value in trackList.json:\n`\"description\" : \"function(featureObject,value) __oc__ return featureObject.parent().get(__sq__note__sq__)__cc__\"`\nSee here for Travis results: https://travis-ci.org/loraine-gueguen/tools-iuc/jobs/541456305","files":null}]}